definitions.definition: A type of comedo , a skin blemish, a type of acne vulgaris , where a pore becomes clogged with a dark, hard, cheesy keratin-filled substance forming a hard black "head" on the skin's surface.
A form of histomoniasis in poultry , characterized by cyanotic discoloration on the bird's head.
A scaup : any of various ducks of the genus Aythya .
